<TITLE> Hasina, Khaleda reciprocate iftar invites, on same day </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, August 27 (bdnews24.com)Prime minister Sheikh Hasina and leader of the opposition Khaleda Zia have invited each other to iftar parties on the same day. The prime minister's party will be held at Gono Bhaban on Saturday, while the BNP chairperson is arranging a party on the same day at the MPs Hostel. "An invitation was delivered to the opposition leader's representative on Wednesday," Abul Kalam Azad, the prime minister's press secretary, told bdnews24.com on Thursday. Meanwhile, Khaleda Zia's press secretary, Maruf Kamal Khan, said an invitation had also been extended to the prime minister to join the BNP's iftar party. b
